Niles to discuss Cyprus' decision to purchase Russian-made S-300
surface-to-air missiles.
</P>
<P>
The U.S., along with several European countries, has expressed
concern about a possible escalation of armaments programs in the
region. Turkey has outrightly condemned the purchase while Athens
has strongly defended Nicosia's decision.
</P>
