amounted to 1,615 in 1996, 506 fewer than the previous year.
</P>
<P>
He said that in addition to enhancing fight against cigarette
smuggling, Hong Kong Customs will continue to cooperate with its
counterparts in the Southeast Asia and exchange information on a
regular arrangements.
</P>
<P>
