<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, January 9 (Xinhua) -- Microsoft launched a new
software package, Microsoft Office 97, here today, which includes
new versions of Microsoft's application software such as Word,
Excel, PowerPoint and Access.
</P>
<P>
The new package also includes a new addition called Microsoft
Outlook, which is said to be a powerful desktop information
manager.
</P>
