<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, January 9 (Xinhua) -- Chinese President Jiang Zemin
met here today with Dr. Peter Wallenberg, a well-known
entrepreneur from Sweden and an old friend of the Chinese people
who has worked diligently to improve Sino-Swedish economic and
trade ties.
</P>
<P>
During the meeting, Jiang said that China's posts and
telecommunications are developing rapidly, and China welcomes
entrepreneurs from Sweden and other countries to conduct
reciprocal cooperation with their Chinese counterparts.
</P>
