pleased to meet with Jiang again, and that the current visit has
enabled him to see the outstanding development in China, and given
him full confidence in China's future development.
</P>
<P>
Wallenberg said he hoped that bilateral friendship and
cooperation between his country and China can be continuously
furthered.
</P>
<P>
Minister of Posts and Telecommunications Wu Jichuan attended
the meeting.
</P>
<P>
Wallenberg started his China tour from January 7 at the
invitation of China's Ministry of Posts and
Telecommunications. 
