<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, January 9 (Xinhua) -- Two Turks were killed, one
missing and 10 others injured in floods caused by heavy rains in
southern and western Turkey, the semi-official Anatolia News
Agency reported today.
</P>
<P>
