people had been injured in the floods caused by two days of
heavy rains in Izmir near the coast of the Aegean Sea.
</P>
<P>
A total of 410 houses and working places have been damaged by
water and 20 houses totally destroyed by the heavy rains in Izmir,
said the paper.
</P>
<P>
It added that schools in the region were closed for one day
because of the heavy rain. 
