<HEADLINE> World Cup Freestyle Skiing Results </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
OTTAWA, January 9 (Xinhua) -- Following are the aerials results
Wednesday at a World Cup freestyle skiing competition in
Mont-Tremblant in Quebec:
</P>
<P>
Men's
</P>
<P>
1. Christian Rijavec, Austria, 238.09
</P>
<P>
2. Lloyd Langlois, Canada, 234.82
