<TEXT>
<P>
BUENOS AIRES, January 8 (Xinhua) -- A forest fire on Tuesday
destroyed about 6,000 hectares of pastureland and woodland in just
three hours in Junin de los Andes in the western Argentine
province of Neuquen.
</P>
