<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, January 8 (Xinhua) -- A Brink armored truck
carrying millions of U. S. dollars flipped over on an Interstate
95 overpass in Miami today, showering thousands of dollars in
currency and coins onto the inner-city neighborhood below.
</P>
<P>
