over Iraq, the United States will continue to maintain a force in
the Middle East large enough to deter Iraqi President Saddam
Hussein.
</P>
<P>
The United Nations imposed sanctions against Iraq following its
invasion of Kuwait in August 1990.
</P>
<P>
