(226,369) and Joe Dumars of Detroit (150,388).
</P>
<P>
At center, Patrick Ewing of the New York Knicks continues to
lead fellow Georgetown big man Alonzo Mourning of the Miami
Heat. Ewing has 285,531 votes, while Mourning has 209,029.
</P>
<P>
The 46th annual NBA All-Star Game will be played at the Gund
Arena in Cleveland with the top two vote-getters at both guard and
forward and the top center on the starting lineup. 
